Playback
Current state: Audio does not play from where seeker is, scrubbing should be real time. Play button and seeker interaction is finicky and does not routinely work. Playback is just of recorded audio, not any harmonies.

Ideal state: Audio plays where seeker is in real time, scrubbing can pause audio but wherever seeker is released is where audio will play. Recorded audio is either of the harmony itself or of the harmony along with the original melody, possibly interactive differing intervals after recording for compare.

